members.description: A domain specific healthcare simulated factory dataset for members

member_id.2021-02-10T22:27:32.519432: a unique id for the member

zipcodes.2021-02-10T22:27:33.246729: Only covering 14 states woth a distribution based on population density

prf_has_phone.2021-02-10T22:27:33.474655: If the person has a phone number on record.

prf_not_call.2021-02-10T22:27:33.535419: If the member has elected not to be called. Must have a phone number

prf_channel_pref.2021-02-10T22:27:33.590381: The channel through which the member can be contacted
prf_channel_pref.2021-02-10T22:27:33.712115: ensure that if prf_not_call is true the preference isn't by phone
prf_channel_pref.2021-02-10T22:27:33.771829: ensure if the member has no phone number the channel preference is not SMS or Phone

prf_service_only.2021-02-10T22:27:33.651235: If the member has elected to be contacted only for servicing purposes

clinical.2021-02-10T22:28:41.516222: a section of clinical data taken from the sample reseach dataset on Diabetes

cln_aptmt_dt.2021-02-10T22:28:41.729260: The date of the appointment when the last clinical health data was taken

cln_pregnancies.2021-02-10T22:28:41.911438: Adjustment to ensure no males are have a value

segment.2021-02-10T22:28:42.623777: The heathcare segment of the member with bias weighting

line_of_business.2021-02-10T22:28:42.944271: The line of business this segment is in

prf_has_email.2021-02-10T22:28:43.143175: If the member has an email address on record

email.2021-02-10T22:28:43.333236: trimming those with email address for over 60s from the persona emails

ins_icd_10_code.2021-02-10T22:28:43.517113: The ICD codes for flu vaccination, Z23 - charable vaccine, Z28 - refused vaccine

ins_cpt_code.2021-02-10T22:28:43.947196: The CPT codes for flu vaccination, Z23 - charable vaccine, Z28 - refused vaccine

ins_cpt_dt.2021-02-10T22:28:44.707616: if had a previous flu shot, a date between 300 and 600 days previous to today

pcp_tax_id.2021-02-10T22:28:47.121165: Taken from the sample healthcare practitioners, matches a city to a practitioner list

is_PCP_auto_assigned.2021-02-10T22:28:47.471157: if the PCP has been auto assigned with a 7/3 positive distribution
